Package: scoring
Type: Package
Title: Credit Scoring tools
Version: 0.1
Author@R: person("Adrien", "Ehrhardt", email = "adrien.ehrhardt@inria.fr",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Adrien Ehrhardt [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Adrien Ehrhardt <adrien.ehrhardt@inria.fr>
Description: This package aims at regroupping essential tools for credit scoring. These statistical tools may be useful for other use-cases as well but were primarly designed for it. First, there are Reject Inference methods' functions,
     although it was shown they do not convey any good asymptotical properties. Second, we build upon the already CRAN-available package "discretization" to and add our own discretization method. Third, we provide a way.
